<html>
<body>
<h1>Pending Tests Module - Report</h1>

Harmful percentage of pending tests defined by user: <%= @percentage_user_input %>
<br><br>
Total of existing tests found: <%= @total_of_existing_tests %>
<br><br>
Total of pending tests found: <%= @total_of_pending_tests %>
<br><br>
Percentage of pending tests: <%= @percentage_of_pending_tests %>
<br><br>
<% if @percentage_of_pending_tests > @percentage_user_input %>
	<div style="background-color:red;border:1px solid black;padding:10px;">
	You should spend some time to review your test suite. It seems you have too many pending tests!
	</div>
<% else %>
	<div style="background-color:green;border:1px solid black;padding:10px;">
	It seems you don't have too many pending tests. Good work! ;)
	</div>
<% end %>
</body>
</html>

